"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-05-olympics-schedule-results-athletics-gymnastics-cycling-21359392\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GBenjoyed a memorable, record-breaking Day 10 at the 2024Olympics, but it was disappointment forSimone Bilesin Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The greatest female gymnast of all time had alreadyclaimed three gold medals at the 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Biles was twice denied gold as shemissed out on a medal altogether in the balance beam finalbefore only managing a silver in the floor final.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Later in the evening, Keely Hodgkinson - one of Team GB's great medal hopes - lived up to expectations, and then some, withgold in a stunning women's 800m final.\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 395, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999963329174, \"rank\": 3.6667762849722273e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson's triumph came afteranother gold medal for Team GB in the velodrome, with Katy Marchant, Emma Finucane and Sophie Capewell breaking three world records in three rides to win thewomen's team sprint.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.7362912761589807, \"rank\": 0.3581581534106004, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\"