ence\": \"The\\u00a0women's 200m final\\u00a0headlines the\\u00a0athletics\\u00a0programme ahead of what promises to be a pulsating night of action at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Goodnight!\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paula Radcliffe appeared to agree with Faith Kipyegon's disqualification after a controversial women's 5,000m Olympic final, in which Beatrice Chebet claimed gold.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paula Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Faith Kipyegon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\"}, {\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beatrice Chebet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipyegon - the former 5,000m world-record holder - clashed with Gudaf Tsegay with around two laps remaining at the Stade de France, which resulted in the Kenyan losing her silver medal.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1418, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gudaf_Tsegay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gudaf Tsegay\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gudaf_Tsegay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gudaf_Tsegay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'To actually grab hold of their arm and move them wide\\u2026 I think that's why the DQ has gone in,' Radcliffe explained on BBC Sport.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1620, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_dwarf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.295507206500419e-19, \"text\": \"DQ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_dwarf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_dwarf\"}, {\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9989199843538196, \"rank\": 0.001081183340576185, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999964784365, \"rank\": 3.488299758923415e-09, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read thefull story here.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB star Keely Hodgkinson said she simply 'could not believe' she had achieved her life-long dream after she became just the third British woman in history to win 800m Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1698, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://