\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were concerning scenes in Spain's semi-final victory over Morocco in the men's football tournament, with the referee having to be replaced due to a nasty-looking injury.\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3492, \"end\": 3497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5434897848844175e-28, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3524, \"end\": 3531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.4775074250534125e-12, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ilgiz Tantashev of Uzbekistan had been selected to officiate the high-stakes clash but hobbled off the field after only 15 minutes following a heavy collision with Spanish defender Marc Pubill.\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3801, \"end\": 3808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9999935864703852, \"rank\": 4.334835389101479e-06, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Glenn Nyberg, the fourth official, came on to replace Tantashev before Spain mounted a second-half comeback to win 2-1.\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3903, \"end\": 3908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5434897848844175e-28, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"