edia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the win, Capewell told BBC Sport: 'I have had my own personal battles and I wish my dad was up there in the stands watching it.\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4375, \"end\": 4384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999964784365, \"rank\": 3.488299758923415e-09, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would be super proud of me.'\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes he would, Sophie \\u2764\\ufe0f  Read thefull story here.\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dina Asher-Smith was lost for words when she did not make the women's 100m final.\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4564, \"end\": 4580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's redeemed herself tonight, finishing second in her semi-final.\", \"from\": 4646, \"to\": 4713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daryll Neita, who agonisingly missed out on a medal in the 100m, also finishes second in her semi.\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4715, \"end\": 4727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daryll_Neita\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daryll Neita\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daryll_Neita\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daryll_Neita\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \