_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 7326, \"end\": 7338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xan_de_Waard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xan De Waard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xan_de_Waard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xan_de_Waard\"}, {\"begin\": 7382, \"end\": 7388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999461301135208, \"rank\": 2.604492182778756e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Netherlands re-took the lead on the stroke of half-time through Luna Fokke, despite GB using a referral after claiming a stick tackle in the lead up to the goal.\", \"from\": 7428, \"to\": 7589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7428, \"end\": 7439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999754289455388, \"rank\": 2.4571557677098266e-05, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7492, \"end\": 7496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8144334876247755e-23, \"text\": \"Luna\", \"types\": [\"Q634\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\"}, {\"begin\": 7512, \"end\": 7514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9909855910178037, \"rank\": 0.009096407239844694, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision wasn't overturned and Fokke scored again in the final quarter to make it 3-1, ending any faint GB hopes of a medal.\", \"from\": 7591, \"to\": 7719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7699, \"end\": 7701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9909855910178037, \"rank\": 0.009096407239844694, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Netherlands progress to the semi-final where they will face one of either China, Argentina, Spain or Belgium.\", \"from\": 7721, \"to\": 7830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7721, \"end\": 7732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999754289455388, \"rank\": 2.4571557677098266e-05, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7795, \"end\": 7800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9363686707109681, \"rank\": 0.06795542319991088, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7802, \"end\": 7811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999995015969, \"rank\": 4.981273719814532e-10, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7813, \"end\": 7818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5434897848844175e-28, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 7822, \"end\": 7829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999564352, \"rank\": 4.358189818008131e-10, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you saw or read about the gymnastics beam finals earlier today, you will know thatUS superstar Simone Biles was pretty hacked off with the crowd.\", \"from\": 7832, \"to\": 7980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7930, \"end\": 7942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were audible gasps at the Bercy Arena after an out-of-sorts Biles fell off the apparatus during an ambitious routine, denying the iconic athlete an eighth gold medal.\", \"from\": 7982, \"to\": 8154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old managed to regain her composure before finishing her routine but had to settle for a fifth-placed finish.\", \"from\": 8156, \"to\": 8277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she appeared to shout at the crowd to 'stop shushing', before turning to teammate Sunisa Lee and asking: 'Why are they all shushing?!\", \"from\": 8279, \"to\": 8416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8365, \"end\": 8375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As soon as I am going they are like \\\"shushing\\\" so much.'\", \"from\": 8417, \"to\": 8473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's now explained in more detail why she was so upset.\", \"from\": 8475, \"to\": 8531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You canread the full story on that here.\", \"from\": 8532, \"to\": 8572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are into the final quarter of the women's hockey quarter-final between Team GB and the Netherlands and it's not looking good.\", \"from\": 8574, \"to\": 8702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8648, \"end\": 8655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999963329174, \"rank\": 3.6667762849722273e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 8664, \"end\": 8675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999754289455388, \"rank\": 2.4571557677098266e-05, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch have just scored another and now lead 3-1 with less than 15 minutes remaining.\", \"from\": 8704, \"to\": 8792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8708, \"end\": 8713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.999999999404281, \"rank\": 5.280776128183641e-10, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"GB need to score at least two to salvage a draw and keep their hopes alive.\", \"from\": 8794, \"to\": 8869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8794, \"end\": 8796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.